&lt;ul class=&quot;[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Create brand identities from scratch: logos, brand guidelines, visual systems, and identity packages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Design all social media assets — posts, stories, covers, carousels, reels, and video content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Edit and produce videos in CapCut: archive material, AI-generated content, stock footage, interviews, and institutional pieces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Build and update sales decks, proposals, internal presentations, and event materials on demand&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Own the visual design of the Arionkoder website in Framer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Build reusable design systems and AI-powered design infrastructure (Claude skills, Canva and CapCut templates) so every launch ships with a consistent visual identity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
