&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;3+ years in marketing design, brand design, or visual communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Strong portfolio showing brand identity, social media, video, and presentation work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Expert in Figma, Google Slides, Canva, and CapCut Pro&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Experience with Framer for web design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Strong sense of typography, layout, hierarchy, and visual clarity&lt;/li&gt;
